learningGoals.technical:
Students acquire a deep understanding of a speciﬁc problem in visualization and medical image analysis, and
technical knowledge about state-of-the-art algorithmic approaches to solving it. This involves problem identiﬁcation;
data processing; selection, design, implementation, and application of suitable algorithms; communication of results.

